Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:06.02,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一番地\N「紺學姊痛哭之夏」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是熱情高漲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可是為了今天特地買的新泳衣和泳圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑太快會跌倒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳圈上破了個洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得軟綿綿的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:00:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然下起暴雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ukobach！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛買的新泳衣啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先擋一下再說啊  作為女高中生…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  作為女人  作為人類都該先擋一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你買咖喱飯吃  你就別哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨  給我來一份咖喱飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  咖喱都賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:51.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}七色的黃昏漸漸降臨
