Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奢侈無緣的貧窮先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我請你去吃一頓夢一般的料理啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.62,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}翻譯：雾代、酱小鱼；校對：飞鱼；Logo特效：Noeru；\N時間、後期、繁化：黑羽侖人；BD後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢人總是這麼臭屁…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很想吃  還是去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這張照片放在枕頭下面入睡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以夢見別人請你吃饕餮大餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:31.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（scence.1  嵐山步的早晨）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:39.45,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「{\c&H00EC57E9}約瑟芬{\r}之夏」原作第二卷{\c&H00BB8695}第19話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的早晨是從帶約瑟芬散步開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨的商店街非常安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像除了我之外的時間都靜止了一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好～早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反季節的颱風好像已經到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說從傍晚開始就要下大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭疼啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡早晨那安靜的商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨的商店街非常安靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像除了我之外的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說颱風要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不把店門前的蔬菜固定好可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我覺得這麼重的話稍微刮點颱風也是吹不走的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說得是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要走在早晨的寂靜之中就會忘卻日常的喧囂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛心靈得到了洗滌一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在常來的堤岸上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晨跑的女士只打一聲招呼就交錯而過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有反季節的颱風要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說夏天的颱風會帶來大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們山森地區會不會有事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  不準備好防災用具可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的應急食品可是有保質期的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾糧估計都硬邦邦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後和往常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一台自動售貨機買一罐咖啡  然後回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:42.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（找零）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意想不到的地方受到了大風災害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在安慰我嗎  約瑟芬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  差不多該回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回那個溫暖的家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  一個接著一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊刷牙一邊出來取報紙  結果被大風刮跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有反季節的颱風要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心大風和暴雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  帶我們出去玩嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海邊就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸可沒有暑假可以放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓姊姊帶你們去市民游泳池怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們兩個  不許這麼任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步鳥  傍晚拜託你帶狗出去散佈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天很忙的啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們全都長得像妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個家裡我的伙伴好像只有約瑟芬一個而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天被有錢人請來捉蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮君  把那隻獨角仙裝進這個金蟲籠裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有兩根柵欄結果讓蟲子跑掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了節約成本！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是純金製的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:31.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（scence.2  嵐山步鳥之夏）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連姊姊也要出門嗎  那游泳池怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊  為什麼連暑假也要去學校啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼～為什麼～為什麼～為什麼～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是想去才去的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無憂無慮的真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧看吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起得那麼早結果還是遲到啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我還以為遲到了  沒想到是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說來補習的…只有我一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既視感！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問這是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我家的狗狗看起來實在是太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想試著編個富有詩意的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不可能被認可啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是期末考試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是補考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補考只是把和期末考試幾乎相同的問題改了下數字而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼分數反而降低了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼問…我也只能說是運氣太差了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是憑感覺做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才清楚地說出了是靠感覺來解題的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是或許會徹底推翻數學理念的奇思妙想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了讓嵐山能夠主動理解  好好下了一番功夫的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  嵐山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探和數學是很相似的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一颳風做木桶生意的就大賺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（意思是原本看起來沒什麼聯繫的事物卻能從中找到因果關係。）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很認真地在說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  也就是要在有限的線索中找出犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將情報和推理有效地結合起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後當所有的矛盾都被解除的時候  犯人也就明確了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相只有一個！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就像推理小說一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過強硬了嗎  我還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探也就是數學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然充滿了幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森秋警官  森秋警官！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到真相了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官  這次不祥的案件…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走進迷宮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛  好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（scence.3  約瑟芬）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天用腦過度了  好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為陪你玩了  所以才遲到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散完步就睡個午覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過暑假也有個暑假的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便亂走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要什麼都吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了會肚子痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  笨葉是指誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是呆鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你們家的狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊  嘲笑別人家的寵物可是很失禮的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看啊  狸貓在帶狸貓散步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸貓帶狸貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  約瑟芬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬她！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你高興什麼啊  你在被嘲笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步鳥  步鳥  快醒醒  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是狗  好像是狸貓  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定回山裡去了  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止給你添麻煩了  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好活下去的  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬？約瑟芬～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到山裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟芬～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裡就是你的家啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颱風都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步鳥還在外面做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}快回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩演寶塚歌劇遊戲吧  畢竟是女孩子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}約瑟芬！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「伸手」的話就要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連「伸手」都不會做的話又要被說是狸貓了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那麼  伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直對牛彈琴  一點會做的樣子都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在這個家裡之後就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家裡的地位排名大概是…這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（墊底）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師教我數學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是就是這種感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好反省可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像比我地位還低的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那個高個子的雄性而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮先生  我剛買了那個熱門電影的DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要在我家的家庭影院一起看啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很閒  又沒有看過  就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是熱門作品的DVD啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有DVD播放機嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮先生  今天也是一副失落的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊？我招待你去我只在冬天使用的別墅如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  雖然不停地在刺我的痛處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是回家也很冷…還是去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  很快就完工了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來幫幫忙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:46.93,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「紺學姊之暗{\c&H0061C27E}怒{\r}」原作第六卷{\c&H002398EF}第49話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動快要結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（空調的設定溫度擅自被下調了3攝氏度）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:35.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冰箱裡的礦泉水擅自被開封了）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（而且還沒有放回冰箱）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（毫無意義的被吹漲的救生圈）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（還有這張臉）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁人家不在的時候隨心所欲的亂動人家東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:56.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（貓被關在外面）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這個時候  步鳥她……）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王  您的飲料  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饅頭  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王  火炬  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炬  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王  火炬  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炬  Poko…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說你們啊  好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要啊  火炬什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著火了  Poko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吊床纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱  動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓬蓬山…著火了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯吃刺身和味增湯可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不是做咖喱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來買東西的時候是打算做咖喱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可禿頭鬍鬚大叔卻給了我一些刺身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個刺身請拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了這個刺身難道會長生不老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  禿頭鬍鬚大叔是真田的老爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  我發現了一個秘方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做煎蛋的時候放砂糖會很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到現在一直做的是什麼樣的煎蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要放反常的砂糖啊  鮮味的秘密就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜味酒啊  哪裡反常了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也放一些砂糖試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會騙你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜的就是好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要放了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是閒著沒事的話就編歌詞去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌詞？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾我也會根據別人寫的歌詞而作曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為明天要和學姊一起去海邊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就以大海為主題吟一句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海鷗好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉好討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By  港口的喬尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當糟糕
