Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  才不是等人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是魚店的那個小子啊
