Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把問號算進去才八個字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…真田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果方便的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海…海邊
